_aChangeLog.text: Changed lighting in sewer to pale
Further optimized the visleafs for even better framerate
Changed the tower to be quadratic for better bot navigation
Removed previous tunnels because they were too messy
Added a big underground canal and tunnel interconnecting two zones
Removed some artifacts which were not necessary
Recalculated and crafted new mesh nav file
Optimized the map for better performance on multiplayer
Added a tower in CT zone too to balance the sniper strikes

_sText:
Map best suitable for gun game or deathmatch. This is third version of the map, i will keep updating it with new stuff and expansion. Using default textures have considerably reduced the download size and server loading time.

1. Underground Canal and Tunnel
3. Various Spawn points
4. Hidden Spots
5. Sniper Spots
6. A tower in each zone for sniper strikes

7. Bot navigation file included
